track.name: Phonograph Blues
comments: I followed the Robert Johnson 'trail' all thru Delta ... found house he was born into ..also his original signature on the marriage license to Virginia (at Courthouse) and more!! ... Son House and Ike Zimmerman taught him a lot!!  see my BLUES shots on flickr (Shein Die)   Man, this is Deep Blues

Why, why are the blues So addicting, almost upon first contact with them?  I guess because they're an essential human condition set to music.  I can't help but think this is called Pornograph Blues, too, based on his singing style, if nothing else.
One of the pieces of the foundation that  the blues house was built on.
the man who sold his soul  to devil to play the Blues....the one with the big B!!! :)
My man - play me some blues. Great history. Legend in his own right.
Como adoro la musica de antaño! Me encanta.
different version i like i like
Bobby J is the fuckin bomb.  Yes, there is enough porno reference here to make a goat hump a rope.  The devil be a stompin' my friend...stompin on that trail.
